  "stages": [
    {
      "id": "study-past-tense",
      "kind": "study",
      "title": "過去式學習",
      "description": "先認識過去式的使用時機，再看規則動詞與不規則動詞的過去式表。",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "callout",
          "title": "過去式重點",
          "body": "過去式用來表示「已經發生過的事」。\n常見時間字有 yesterday、last night、last week、ago。"
        },
        {
          "type": "table",
          "title": "現在式與過去式",
          "columns": ["句型", "英文", "中文"],
          "rows": [
            ["現在式", "Tom cleans the room every day.", "Tom 每天打掃房間。"],
            ["過去式", "Tom cleaned the room yesterday.", "Tom 昨天打掃了房間。"],
            ["現在式", "Amy writes a letter.", "Amy 寫信。"],
            ["過去式", "Amy wrote a letter last night.", "Amy 昨晚寫了一封信。"]
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "title": "規則動詞變化規則",
          "body": "大部分規則動詞直接加 -ed，例如 play -> played。\n字尾是 e 時只加 -d，例如 like -> liked。\n子音加 y 結尾時，把 y 改成 i 再加 -ed，例如 study -> studied。\n短母音 + 子音結尾時，常把最後一個子音重複再加 -ed，例如 stop -> stopped。"
        },
        {
          "type": "example-list",
          "title": "過去式例句",
          "items": [
            {
              "english": "The boy played soccer yesterday.",
              "chinese": "那個男孩昨天踢足球。"
            },
            {
              "english": "Amy went to the library last Sunday.",
              "chinese": "Amy 上週日去了圖書館。"
            },
            {
              "english": "We watched the movie last night.",
              "chinese": "我們昨晚看了那部電影。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "table",
          "title": "不規則動詞的過去式",
          "columns": ["原形", "中文", "過去式"],
          "rows": [
            ["be", "是、在", "was / were"],
            ["have", "有", "had"],
            ["do", "做", "did"],
            ["go", "去", "went"],
            ["come", "來", "came"],
            ["see", "看見", "saw"],
            ["say", "說", "said"],
            ["get", "得到", "got"],
